../../planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:5:This is a more honest version of the tensor-alignment instinct than most. It explicitly names the full stretching term, it brings harmonic far-field debt into the chain instead of hiding it, and it gives the negative branch real status.
../../planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:15:- The representation package is not the main unresolved choice. The real unresolved choice is the theorem-level endpoint. "Full stretching control," "pressure-Hessian/strain defect control," and "harmonic-moment cancellation" are not three versions of one bottleneck; they are three different proof architectures.
../../planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:26:- The candidate menu is crowded with familiar descendants of the alignment and restricted-Euler literature: eigenvalue-gap combinations, vorticity-to-eigenframe alignment, pressure/strain misalignment, and defect observables. A table can make these look newly systematized without making them new.
../../planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:31:The danger is that Step 2 produces a polished audit table of quantities that are definable, invariant, and narratively compelling, but still do not change the sign, size, or summability of the actual stretching term. That is classification, not leverage.
../../planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:38:- The local/harmonic split can be written down explicitly, but explicit splitting is not close to closure. The far-field harmonic data can alter the pressure Hessian without respecting the local geometric picture that made the observable attractive.
../../planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:70:The chain freezes representation, bottleneck vocabulary, and observables before it fixes where the route is supposed to cash out mathematically. That invites post hoc success criteria. A tensor route should have to name the exact inequality, continuation criterion, or contradiction line before it starts optimizing observables.
../../planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:78:This branch lives directly next to existing work on strain-vorticity alignment, eigenvalue geometry, restricted Euler defects, pressure-Hessian modeling, and conditional regularity criteria. Novelty screening belongs before the observable shortlist becomes emotionally favored, not after.
../../planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-01.md:94:What is genuinely strong is the honesty of the design. The chain explicitly names the full stretching term, forces confrontation with harmonic moments, rejects self-induced caricatures, and leaves real room for obstruction as the final product.
