../../planning-runs/run-001/judgments/chain-03.md:89:- The probability of a presentable negative result is materially higher, because the attack has isolated a concrete obstruction: local near-Beltrami structure may only control a local/self-induced part of stretching while leaving the scale-critical nonlocal remainder untouched.
