../../planning-runs/run-010/selected/chain-01.md:5:Geometry remains the most mission-facing candidate mechanism, but the old neutral-Eulerian package is already weak. This chain is live only if one openly declared package change turns local Beltrami deficit, direction coherence, or tube persistence into a theorem-facing bridge to a Constantin-Fefferman-type criterion or to full-stretching reduction, without hiding the gain inside the localization itself.
