+   Constantin-Fefferman-type criterion by default, or one named
+   full-stretching contradiction target if the local record clearly supports it
+   better;
+2. one gain currency only, together with the minimum non-cosmetic gain that
+   would count in that same currency;
+3. one candidate proposition, contradiction line, or insertion claim that can
+   be written before any package choice, or a direct source-based reason that
+   no such claim is honestly writable;
+4. one admissibility decision only:
+   direct suitable-weak / LEI definability if the local record supports it,
+   otherwise one named proxy class together with the exact bridge burden back
+   to the theorem floor;
+5. one closest live geometric prior-art comparator only, with the exact shared
+   structure already present there and the sharpest local source on whether the
+   claimed delta is already absorbed; and
+6. the strongest repository-local evidence for an immediate Step-1 kill
+   condition:
+   endpoint-free obstruction,
+   theorem-floor obstruction,
+   descriptive-convenience obstruction,
+   or prior-art absorption before package selection.
