+  cheaper criterion input than the prior-art Constantin-Fefferman comparator,
+  without importing stronger `nabla xi` control, then it could insert into a
+  Constantin-Fefferman-type criterion.
+  No present-tense package-free theorem-facing claim is currently supported by
+  the required local sources.
